{
  "metadata": {
    "masechet_en": "Bekhorot",
    "masechet_he": "בכורות",
    "daf": "22B",
    "perek_title": "הלוקח בהמה",
    "perek_number": 3
  },
  "english": [
    "<b>into one hundred</b> <i>se’a</i> of <b>pure, non-sacred</b> produce, <b>Rabbi Eliezer says: Let</b> one <i>se’a</i> <b>be lifted</b> from the mixture <b>and</b> left to <b>rot</b> as impure <i>teruma</i>, <b>as I say: The <i>se’a</i> that fell is the <i>se’a</i> that arose?</b>",
    "<b>And the Rabbis say: Let</b> the <i>se’a</i> of <i>teruma</i> <b>arise</b> and be nullified by the one hundred <i>se’a</i> of non-sacred produce, and then all one hundred and one <i>se’a</i> will be considered non-sacred. Nevertheless, the mixture may not be allowed to come in contact with water, so that it does not become susceptible to ritual impurity, <b>and</b> therefore it must <b>be eaten dry or roasted. Or</b> alternatively, <b>it may be kneaded with fruit juice,</b> which does not render a substance susceptible to impurity. <b>Or</b> alternatively, if one wants to knead it with water, <b>it may divided</b> into <b>small batches, provided that</b> there is <b>not an egg-bulk</b> of <i>teruma</i> <b>in a single</b> batch, as an egg-bulk is the minimum volume needed for food to be susceptible to contracting impurity.",
    "<b>And it is taught in that regard:</b> Concerning <b>those</b> one hundred <i>se’a</i> of <b>non-sacred</b> produce,"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לְמֵאָה חוּלִּין טְהוֹרִין, רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר אוֹמֵר: תֵּירוֹם",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְתֵרָקֵב, שֶׁאֲנִי אוֹמֵר: הִיא סְאָה שֶׁנָּפְלָה הִיא",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סְאָה שֶׁעָלְתָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וַחֲכָמִים אוֹמְרִים: תַּעֲלֶה, וְתֵיאָכֵל",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נִיקּוּדִים, אוֹ קְלָיוֹת, אוֹ תִּילּוֹשׁ בְּמֵי פֵירוֹת,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹ תִּתְחַלֵּק לְעִיסּוֹת, וּבִלְבַד שֶׁלֹּא יְהֵא",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּמָקוֹם אֶחָד כְּבֵיצָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְתָנֵי עֲלַהּ: אוֹתָן חוּלִּין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>לְמֵאָה חוּלִּין טְהוֹרִין.</b> שלא הוכשרו ולא טימאתן בנפילתה: <b>תירום.</b> ירום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "משם סאה ותירקב כדין תרומה טמאה שאני אומר כו' ותרומה טמאה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אסורה באכילה: <b>תַּעֲלֶה</b> תיבטל ותיאכל עם חוליה ומשום גזירה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "יתן דמים לכהנים או ירים ממנה סאה ותאכל לכהנים: <b>נִיקּוּדִים.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ביובש כמו יָבֵ֖שׁ הָיָ֥ה (<a href=\"https://www.sefaria.org/Joshua.9.5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sefaria-ref=\"Joshua.9.5\">יהושע ט׳:ה׳</a>).",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דעכשיו אע\"ג שיש בה טמאה וטהורה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אין מטמאה את הטהורה בלא הכשר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וטמאה בטילה בטהורה ותיאכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ניקודים: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">וקליות</span></b> נמי דלא מיתכשרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולא מקבלי טומאה: <b>אוֹ תִּילּוֹשׁ בְּמֵי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>פֵירוֹת</b> כמו מי תפוחים ותותים דמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פירות אין מכשירין: <b>אוֹתָן חוּלִּין <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לר&#x27;</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אליעזר</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">מה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">תהא</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">עליהם</span>.</b> דלרבנן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הא אמרינן בכולהו בין חולין בין תרומה יאכל נקודים או קליות:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bekhorot 22b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    }
  ],
